CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 24, 2014

[Cite as 02/24/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-637.]

*1422MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1893. State ex rel. Griffin v. Sheldon.

In Habeas Corpus. This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of petitioner’s motions for default judgment and to give notice of violation of R.C. 2725.24. It is ordered by the court that the motions are denied as moot.
